text: Good morning y’all. We’ve delicious bagels on walnut.
Class is over! Thank you all so much for your help. I could tell they all really loved the visit, and we couldn't have done it without you!
Quote from a student: "This place is like OMSI!"
Oh I can’t tell you how many oogly eyes I saw when we were demoing/touring the space. Thank you all again. You’re making dreams come true!
